Roll up each piece of mackerel and secure with a cocktail stick.Heat the olive oil in a small frying pan over a medium heat. Add the mackerel and fry for two minutes on each side, then remove from the pan and put onto a slice of griddled ciabatta.To make the rocket pesto, place all the ingredients into a food processor and blend until smooth.To serve, pour the rocket pesto over the mackerel rolls.